text: Kangana Ranaut Rangoon music review: Not as… Rangoon music review: Not as brilliant as Haider’s, music for Shahid, Kangana and Saif’s love triangle pays fitting tribute to the ’40s If you are someone who believe has a refined taste in music, the music of Rangoon may certainly appeal to you, as Vishal Bharadwaj does full justice to the era in which the movie is based. By Sreeju Sudhakaran | Published: January 23, 2017 8:40 am
